name: Wolfgang Gartner
description: '''Joseph Thomas Youngman''' (born March 17, 1982), better known by his stage name '''Wolfgang Gartner''', is an [[Americans|American]] DJ and music producer. Much of his music prior to 2010 was released through his own record label, Kindergarten, but he signed with [[Ultra Records]] in 2010 and [[Ministry of Sound]] in the UK in 2011.
